title: S6: The EU's plan to catch up on artificial intelligence
description: While the US and China have been setting the pace when it comes to Artificial Intelligence, the European Union seems to be lagging behind. What are the Commission's plans to finally catch up? Will AI increase the gap between big and small companies? Nicholas Barrett asked Julia Anderson and Guntram Wolff
itunes:author: Bruegel
dc:creator: Bruegel
